| accessdate = 2007-02-26
}}&lt;br/&gt;* {{cite web
| url = http://www.cricinfo.com/db/ARCHIVE/2002-03/AUS_LOCAL/STATS/WA/FC_2002-03_BAT_HIGHEST_AVS_WA.html
